Troubleshooting
===============

Q: FreeDink freezes when trying to play a sound or music.

A: SDL is known to freeze in some situations when you have
   /dev/sequencer available and /etc/timidity/timidity.cfg isn't
   present. An easy fix is to install Timidity++ (see BUILD).

   More information at
   http://bugs.debian.org/cgi-bin/bugreport.cgi?bug=369670
